org.ctoolkit.restapi.client.adaptee

Interface InsertExecutorAdaptee<M>

  • Type Parameters:
    M - the concrete type of request's model object to work with
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    RestExecutorAdaptee<M>

    public interface InsertExecutorAdaptee<M>
    The adaptee interface to provide execute implementation for REST POST operation on top of concrete type.

    Aurel Medvegy
